/UnityProject/[Aa]sets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/VisualScripting.Core/Property Providers
/UnityProject/[Aa]ssets/Unity.VisualScripting.Generated/VisualScripting.Core/Property Providers.meta

# Auto-generated scenes by play mode tests
/UnityProject/[Aa]ssets/[Ii]nit[Tt]est[Ss]cene*.unity*